description:
This is a fork of websocket-sharp with support for NTLM/Kerberos Proxy authentication.

websocket-sharp provides the WebSocket protocol client and server.
It supports:

- RFC 6455

- WebSocket Client and Server

- Per-message Compression extension

- Secure Connection

- HTTP Authentication (Basic/Digest)

- Query String, Origin header and Cookies

- Connecting through the HTTP Proxy server

- .NET 3.5 or later (includes compatible)
releaseNotes:
Fork of websocket-sharp at commit 0eec6595a6cc26abf684a50343e29b3d3a3e18ea. 

 - Add websocket support for Proxy enabled with NTLM and Kerberos authentication.

 - Pending pull request in progress: https://github.com/sta/websocket-sharp/pull/148

 - This Package will not be required if pull request is successful, for now package is available to share changes.
title: websocket-sharp-Proxy-NTLM-Kerberos
